  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dda\u0da9\u0dd3\u0dba\u0dbb\u0dca 9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dda\u0da2\u0dbb\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db0\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d8b\u0dc3\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "9 Brigadiers are promoted to the rank of Major General",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "09 senior officers of the rank of Brigadier have been promoted to the rank of Major General. These promotions are being done by the Commander in Chief of the Armed Forces, President Ranil Wickramasinghe on the recommendation of the Commander of the Army Lt. Gen. Vikum Liyanage and the Ministry of Defense.",
        "Brigadier Shewantha Kulatunga, Sri Lanka Engineer Corps, Commander of 23 Division",
        "Brigadier Mihidu Perera of the Sri Lankan Infantry who is on an overseas course",
        "Director of Ordnance Services Sri Lanka Army Ordnance Corps Brigadier Indrajith Vithanachchi",
        "Director of Staff Duties Sri Lanka Artillery Brigadier Manjula Kariyawasam",
        "Brigadier Mahinda Ranasinghe of the Special Forces attached to the Presidential Security Division",
        "The senior officers were accordingly promoted to the rank of Major General"
      ],
